        <mxCell id="import_body" value="1. file_picker → bytes&#xa;2. excel.decodeBytes(bytes)&#xa;3. Normalize row text&#xa;4. Resolve ID via aliases.json&#xa;   → if not found: isCustom = true&#xa;5. Upsert in Drift transaction:&#xa;   Vehicles → Compartments&#xa;   → EquipmentItems → Assignments&#xa;6. Show post-import review prompt&#xa;   for all custom-created items" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FBE9E7;strokeColor=#E65100;fontColor=#1A1A1A;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;arcSize=4;" vertex="1" parent="1">
